/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3cdd3d87747dc3ce4b82cd42cf1fd24f729b36f","tid":1015761,"uid":126083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T11:52:33.000Z","msg":"睇個software list似係讀game design?如果係咁咁可以睇睇最少用gtx 1070嘅laptop，做到VR之類嗰啲都負荷到，見你筆直少﹐可以睇睇呢部<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/HP-Refresh-i7-8750H-5HS21UA-ABA/dp/B07H9XPF1S/ref=sr_1_3?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1549885020&amp;sr=8-3&amp;keywords=HP+Omen+1070\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FHP-Refresh-i7-8750H-5HS21UA-ABA%2Fdp%2FB07H9XPF1S%2Fref%3Dsr_1_3%3Fie%3DUTF8%26qid%3D1549885020%26sr%3D8-3%26keywords%3DHP%2BOmen%2B1070&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BA2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=4e8f93c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/HP-Refresh-i7-8750H-5HS21UA-ABA/dp/B07H9XPF1S/ref=sr_1_3?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1549885020&amp;sr=8-3&amp;keywords=HP+Omen+1070</a><br />\n<br />\n一定要買最少16GB ram嘅laptop，maya，unity，UE等等嘅software都勁食ram，另外用到substance painter同zbrush就最好買埋個drawing tablet，有筆直啲就買cintiq，冇乜㗎話副廠都唔差。<br />\n<br />\n我建議唔使買到差唔多兩萬嘅laptop，留啲錢買幫助做嘢同學嘢嘅配件同software好啲（畫板，VR headset，好嘅滑鼠等等，另外zbrush冇學生免費版只有discounted offer）﹐\b但如果有筆直㗎話可以買啲輕薄啲嘅，例如msi gs75，同埋買新啲，有埋RTX card嘅，對game development都幾大幫助，不過上面介紹嗰部HP嘅都有thunderbolt 3頭，可以用外置display card，應該都夠用"},{"pid":"a11138382665073f366e00d2205aa9acb421f7e2","tid":1015761,"uid":161814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T12:22:47.000Z","msg":"急唔急要？可以search下HP zbook, 每年poly 開學都有discount 原價2萬幾減到12-13k<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果我冇記錯，2018好似係跟quadro P1000顯卡, 8th i7 u"},{"pid":"d2c2e1cdf879d83041d641e188ddbaae2638278f","tid":1015761,"uid":161814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3cdd3d87747dc3ce4b82cd42cf1fd24f729b36f","tid":1015761,"uid":126083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T11:52:33.000Z","msg":"睇個software list似係讀game design?如果係咁咁可以睇睇最少用gtx 1070嘅laptop，做到VR之類嗰啲都負荷到，見你筆直少﹐可以睇睇呢部<a href=